    "title": "First Person + Negation",
    "explanation": "Annette est ma maman. The word ma means 'my' — Annette belongs to the speaker.\n\nNow watch for ne...pas: Ce n'est pas le chat. The two words ne and pas wrap around the verb to deny it.\n\nRe-read and find every ma/mon. Who is speaking? Then find ne...pas. What gets denied?"
